Date: Sat, 7 Nov 2020 11:30:56 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] [FIX] mail: make the current user member of the created
 channel

Purpose
=======
Before, by default, if a user create a channel, he will not be member
of this channel.

After, the current user will always be member of the new channel.

Task 1963414
---
 addons/mail/i18n/mail.pot          | 24 ++++++++++++++++
 addons/mail/models/mail_channel.py | 46 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
 2 files changed, 67 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

